Problem Statement
Many elderly patients and individuals face difficulties in:
Managing medical records
Booking appointments quickly
Getting help during emergencies
Keeping family members informed
This project solves these issues by providing a connected healthcare ecosystem.
💡 Solution
A centralized platform where:
Patients can manage their health
Doctors can treat patients digitally
Hospitals can manage operations
Family members can monitor patient health
👥 User Roles & Features
👤 Patient
Create and manage account
Book, reschedule, or cancel appointments
View prescriptions and medical history
Add family members
Trigger emergency alerts
Join video consultations
👨‍👩‍👧 Family Member
Access patient data (with permission)
View appointments and prescriptions
Receive emergency alerts
Track medicine reminders
👨‍⚕️ Doctor
View and manage appointments
Access patient medical history
Add prescriptions
Conduct video consultations
Mark appointments as completed
🏥 Hospital
Manage doctors (add/remove/view)
Manage appointments (approve/reject/assign/reschedule)
Handle emergency alerts
Monitor system activity
🔑 Key Features
📅 Appointment Management
Book and manage appointments
Assign doctors
Track appointment status
💊 Prescription System
Doctors can create and send prescriptions
Patients can view prescription history
🎥 Video Consultation
Doctors and patients can connect remotely
Enables treatment without visiting the hospital
🚨 Emergency Alert System
One-click emergency button
Sends alerts to:
Family members
Hospital
Shares patient location for quick response
👨‍👩‍👧 Family Access System
Patients can add multiple family members
Family members get limited access
Helps monitor elderly patients
🔐 Multi-User Login System
Role-based login (Patient, Doctor, Hospital, Family)
Secure authentication (Email/Password, OTP)
Role-based dashboards
🔄 System Flow
Patient registers and logs in
Patient books an appointment
Hospital approves and assigns a doctor
Doctor views appointment and consults patient
Doctor adds prescription
Patient and family can view updates
In emergencies, alerts are sent instantly
🔒 Security Features
Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)
OTP verification
Secure authentication
Data privacy restrictions
🧠 Tech Stack (Example)
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript / React
Backend: Node.js / Django
Database: MongoDB / MySQL
Authentication: Firebase / JWT
Video Call: WebRTC / Zoom API
🚀 Future Enhancements
AI-based health recommendations
Wearable device integration
Live ambulance tracking
Multi-language support